{"word":"προτακτέος","slug":"προτακτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προτακτέος</b></el> <el>(προτακτέος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:προτάσσω'><el>προτάσσω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one must place in front</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>one must prefer</i>, <el>τί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}